=== DoD: Lookup RPC validates token format before hashing ===
Migration 20260311000000 drops and recreates lookup_share_token_v1 with format
guard before extensions.digest() is called. Rules: shr_ prefix required, body
must be exactly 64 lowercase hex chars [0-9a-f], total length == 68.
=== DoD: Invalid tokens fail immediately before DB lookup ===
Tests 1-5 prove: NULL token, missing prefix, short token, uppercase hex body,
and non-hex body all return NOT_FOUND before hashing occurs.
=== DoD: Malformed tokens return identical response shape as invalid tokens ===
Tests 6-7 prove: malformed token response code and error message are identical
to a nonexistent valid-format token. No format information leaked to callers.
=== DoD: Valid format token proceeds to lookup stage ===
Test 9 proves: a well-formed shr_-prefixed token with valid hex body resolves
OK against a seeded share_tokens row.
